title: Oceansize.EPs+Singles.2001-2009.FLAC
description:
----- Oceansize.EPs+Singles.2001-2009.FLAC ---------------------------

This is a collection of all EPs and singles produced by Oceansize from 2001-2009. It contains FLAC tracks and cue sheets. Three of the albums weren't ripped by me, indicated with a *.

----- Contents -------------------------------------------------------

2001 - A Very Still Movement *
2002 - Relapse *
2003 - One Day All This Could Be Yours
2003 - Remember Where You Are
2004 - Catalyst
2004 - Music for Nurses *
2005 - Heaven Alive
2006 - New Pin (2 versions)
2009 - Home & Minor

----------------------------------------------------------------------

If you like their music, please support Oceansize by buying the albums. Also, check out Vennart's first solo album, The Demon Joke
